3/|archivedate=October 30, 2019}}\n*{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2019-11-18/p/3/|title=\u9031\u9593 \u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 (2019\u5e7411\u670818\u65e5\u4ed8)|website=Oricon|language=ja|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113024740/https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2019-11-18/p/3/|archivedate=November 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''[[Hello Chapter 2: Hello, Strange Place]]''\n|\n* Released: November 19, 2019 {{small|(KOR)}} \n* Label: C9 Entertainment\n* Formats: CD, digital download, streaming\n| 4 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n* KOR: 76,037<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=2019&hitYear=2019&termGbn=year|script-title=ko:2019\ub144 Album Chart|trans-title= 2019 Album Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|accessdate=January 10, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Singles ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of singles, with selected chart positions, showing year released, and album name\n! rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width:12em;\"| Title\n! rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width:2em;\"| Year\n! colspan=\"2\"| Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Album\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\"| KOR\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Gaon Digital Chart|Gaon]]<br><ref>Charted songs on [[Gaon Digital Chart]]:</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[K-pop Hot 100|Hot]]<br><ref>Charted songs on [[K-pop Hot 100]]:</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Movie Star\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2019\n| \u2014 || \u2014 \n|''Hello Chapter 1: Hello, Stranger''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"My New World\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|''Hello Chapter 1: Hello, Stranger (Japanese version)''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Numb\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 \n|''Hello Chapter 2: Hello, Strange Place''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Revival\"\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2020\n| \u2014 || \u2014 \n|''Revival''\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"font-size:8pt\"