{"title_page": "Hiroki Bandai", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese football player|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2016}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Hiroki Bandai<br/>\u842c\u4ee3 \u5b8f\u6a39\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Hiroki Bandai\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1986|2|19}}\n|birth_place=[[Sendai]], [[Miyagi Prefecture|Miyagi]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.84}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=[[ReinMeer Aomori]]\n|clubnumber=30\n|youthyears1=2001\u20132003|youthclubs1=[[Fukushima Higashi High School]]\n|years1=2004\u20132007|clubs1=[[Vegalta Sendai]]|caps1=107|goals1=21\n|years2=2008\u20132009|clubs2=[[J\u00fabilo Iwata]]|caps2=27|goals2=3\n|years3=2010|clubs3=[[Sagan Tosu]]|caps3=26|goals3=2\n|years4=2011|clubs4=[[Thespakusatsu Gunma|Thespa Kusatsu]]|caps4=35|goals4=8\n|years5=2012\u20132015|clubs5=[[Montedio Yamagata]]|caps5=94|goals5=11\n|years6=2016\u20132017|clubs6=[[Mito HollyHock]]|caps6=14|goals6=1\n|years7=2017\u20132018|clubs7=[[AC Nagano Parceiro]]|caps7=38|goals7=7\n|years8=2019\u2013|clubs8=[[ReinMeer Aomori]]|caps8=|goals8=\n|totalcaps=341|totalgoals=53\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n{{Medal|Team|[[Montedio Yamagata]]}}\n{{Medal|RU|[[Emperor's Cup]]|[[2014 Emperor's Cup|2014]]}}\n|club-update=end of 2018 season\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n{{Nihongo|'''Hiroki Bandai'''|\u842c\u4ee3 \u5b8f\u6a39|Bandai Hiroki|born 19 February 1986}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>{{J.League player}}</ref>\n\n==Club statistics==\n''Updated to 31 January 2019''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/2016J1-J2-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411335/ref=pd_cp_14_1?ie=UTF8&refRID=1N6B11BBGDQ32GYF7MWJ